thread.title: Martin A - Southampton
thread.title_full: Official Car Mats reviewed by Martin A - Southampton

author: Martin A - Southampton
title: Martin A - Southampton
text:
Ordered a pair of Luxury car mats and the product arrived on time - kept advised by email at each stage of order and dispatch. Arrived on time.
Great quality, good price and first class service. Also very helpful with sorting out my mistake with retaining clips by supplying a solution within 24hrs . Would not hesitate to recommend or purchase again from this company.
